{"tid":853474,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"焦慮症有冇得醫","createTime":"2018-10-08T15:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T01:40:31.000Z","uid":118653,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"39f7b8d7666279779d70461671ae535b4b24523e","tid":853474,"uid":118653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T15:17:53.000Z","msg":"係咪一定要食藥？<br />\n我每天都過得好痛苦😖，活在惶恐之中😫😫<br />\n因為父親經常唔舒服，每次唔舒服就去醫院，令到我慢慢形成左好嚴重的焦慮症，我覺得自己已經好嚴重，又失眠又食唔到野，大家可唔可以救下我...<br />\n有諗過一走了之，搬出去住，但知道只是逃避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aaf3549a35c52c0b94b57f28474f309ae525a53","tid":853474,"uid":171449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:06:01.000Z","msg":"有得醫，睇醫生先"},{"pid":"42b387c745bfda785d4cfcb54e4dba38e0619fd0","tid":853474,"uid":204644,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:11:17.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始食藥個幾月，暫時無乜特別感覺，同未睇醫生差唔多，希望盡快有好轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有呢個病最慘係身邊既人覺得你好少事，覺得你其實可以控制到。如果你地身邊都有呢類人，盡量唔好咁多意見喇，唔係只會令對方更多壓力，覺得係自己有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1afea88308c20432bbd480e1cda783e162a54757","tid":853474,"uid":36603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:11:19.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n三日加埋先瞓到5個鐘 又好無胃口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332b0cf657da2fdcd69a24446379ea9154a5f2f1","tid":853474,"uid":118653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T16:25:55.000Z","msg":"大家同道中人，不如分享一下經歷，大家互勉之。"},{"pid":"c90fd70163e8d8b29d05fd86c499190d6633ecc8","tid":853474,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T01:40:31.000Z","msg":"認知行為治療"}]}